[
  {
    "startTime": 4.935,
    "endTime": 7.103,
    "text": "All rise."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.103,
    "endTime": 9.107,
    "text": "The court of holidays is now in session."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.107,
    "endTime": 25.889,
    "text": "Presiding at the bench are New Year's, Valentine's, Easter, Halloween, Thanksgiving, and chief justice Christmas."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.889,
    "endTime": 28.5,
    "text": "Thank you, Tax Day. You may be seated."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.2,
    "endTime": 35.3,
    "text": "As you know, the yearly calendar has become bloated with holidays."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.3,
    "endTime": 40.9,
    "text": "We are gathered to hear the pleas of all minor holidays to determine if they will be allowed to stay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.9,
    "endTime": 44.941,
    "text": "April Fool's will be taking minutes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.941,
    "endTime": 45.876000000000005,
    "text": "-Totally.  -All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.0,
    "endTime": 50.914,
    "text": "First on the list, we shall hear from the daylight saving twins."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.914,
    "endTime": 53.817,
    "text": "Boo. Nobody likes you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.817,
    "endTime": 55.285,
    "text": "Hold on, now!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.285,
    "endTime": 56.919,
    "text": "Fall back is very popular."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.92,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "I say we keep her and sentence spring forward to death."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 61.8,
    "text": "Oh, great idea."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.8,
    "endTime": 65.295,
    "text": "If you get rid of her, you'll have to get rid of me, too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.664,
    "endTime": 69.0,
    "text": "All right, fine. You may stay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.0,
    "endTime": 72.5,
    "text": "We want the record to show that we formally declare you stupid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.5,
    "endTime": 75.572,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.572,
    "endTime": 77.007,
    "text": "Next is Black Friday."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.007,
    "endTime": 77.641,
    "text": "Move."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.641,
    "endTime": 79.5,
    "text": "Get out of my way, I was here first."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.5,
    "endTime": 81.444,
    "text": "No! She can't be here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.444,
    "endTime": 86.917,
    "text": "I filed a restraining order; you have to stay at least one day away from me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.917,
    "endTime": 88.218,
    "text": "He's right, Black Friday."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.218,
    "endTime": 91.62100000000001,
    "text": "You need to stay in your designated place on the calendar."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.621,
    "endTime": 92.756,
    "text": "Mmmm, No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.756,
    "endTime": 94.057,
    "text": "Okay, whatever you want."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.057,
    "endTime": 94.424,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.159,
    "endTime": 99.763,
    "text": "Next is Chinese New Year."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.763,
    "endTime": 101.364,
    "text": "You!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.364,
    "endTime": 102.866,
    "text": "Hello, New Year's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.866,
    "endTime": 103.633,
    "text": "He has got to go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.633,
    "endTime": 105.068,
    "text": "We can't have two starts to the year. It's confusing!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.303,
    "endTime": 107.47,
    "text": "I was here first!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.47,
    "endTime": 108.371,
    "text": "I'm more popular!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.371,
    "endTime": 111.173,
    "text": "I have a parade of dragons!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.174,
    "endTime": 112.00800000000001,
    "text": "Dang it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.008,
    "endTime": 114.377,
    "text": "All right, All right! I've heard enough. You may stay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.245,
    "endTime": 116.679,
    "text": "Come on, Valentine's, back me up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.68,
    "endTime": 118.14800000000001,
    "text": "Oh, I think they both should go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.148,
    "endTime": 119.214,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.215,
    "endTime": 122.686,
    "text": "No one meets my expectations."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.686,
    "endTime": 125.0,
    "text": "All right, next on the list: PI Day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.0,
    "endTime": 126.0,
    "text": "Approved!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.289,
    "endTime": 127.29,
    "text": "Goodness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.29,
    "endTime": 130.16,
    "text": "Okay, we haven't cut anyone from the list; who else is coming in today?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.16,
    "endTime": 131.761,
    "text": "ST. Patrick's Day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.761,
    "endTime": 132.362,
    "text": "No, No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.362,
    "endTime": 135.031,
    "text": "People need a special day to pretend that they're Irish."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.031,
    "endTime": 135.49800000000002,
    "text": "Oh, that's right, that's right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.733,
    "endTime": 137.734,
    "text": "Cinco de Mayo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.734,
    "endTime": 141.304,
    "text": "People need a special day to pretend that they're Mexican, too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.304,
    "endTime": 142.939,
    "text": "Election Day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.939,
    "endTime": 147.643,
    "text": "People need a special day to pretend that they voted!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.644,
    "endTime": 149.446,
    "text": "All right, what about Groundhog's Day?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.446,
    "endTime": 152.281,
    "text": "Oh, if we lose him, do we lose the Bill Murray movie as well?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.282,
    "endTime": 153.049,
    "text": "It's not worth the risk."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.049,
    "endTime": 153.583,
    "text": "Nuh-uh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.583,
    "endTime": 154.651,
    "text": "Have we thought about Mother's Day?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.885,
    "endTime": 159.022,
    "text": "Shame on you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.022,
    "endTime": 159.923,
    "text": "Father's Day?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.923,
    "endTime": 160.857,
    "text": "Yeah, we could lose that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.857,
    "endTime": 161.224,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.224,
    "endTime": 162.759,
    "text": "Yep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.759,
    "endTime": 163.76,
    "text": "What about Labor day?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.76,
    "endTime": 164.393,
    "text": "No way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.394,
    "endTime": 165.028,
    "text": "Why not?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.028,
    "endTime": 166.396,
    "text": "It's a day off of work!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.396,
    "endTime": 168.131,
    "text": "Then shouldn't we call it No Labor Day?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.131,
    "endTime": 169.132,
    "text": "That's what I think."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.132,
    "endTime": 171.268,
    "text": "There's more to a holiday than just getting the day off."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.268,
    "endTime": 173.069,
    "text": "You would say that, Halloween."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.069,
    "endTime": 174.70399999999998,
    "text": "Look who's talking, Valentine's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.704,
    "endTime": 175.405,
    "text": "How dare you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.405,
    "endTime": 177.274,
    "text": "Would you dare talk to me that way?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.974,
    "endTime": 178.60799999999998,
    "text": "All right, order, order!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.909,
    "endTime": 183.146,
    "text": "Let us just review the minutes and then make an informed decision."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.146,
    "endTime": 185.27999999999997,
    "text": "April Fool's!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.281,
    "endTime": 188.618,
    "text": "I haven't been taking any minutes!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.618,
    "endTime": 191.488,
    "text": "Whoo!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.457,
    "endTime": 195.792,
    "text": "Thanks for watching, everyone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.792,
    "endTime": 199.496,
    "text": "Comment below on how Christmas is your favorite holiday."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.496,
    "endTime": 201.965,
    "text": "You mean, if it's your favorite holiday."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.965,
    "endTime": 203.667,
    "text": "Ha-Ha! Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.667,
    "endTime": 205.502,
    "text": "Please subscribe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.27,
    "endTime": 208.904,
    "text": "Do it again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.905,
    "endTime": 209.372,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.372,
    "endTime": 210.34,
    "text": "Got it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.34,
    "endTime": 212.007,
    "text": "We're all going to die one day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.008,
    "endTime": 214.411,
    "text": "I'm going to die first."
  }
]